  <!-- WHY ANNUAL -->
  <section class="pf-section" style="background:#f8fafc;">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>Why Every Formby Boiler Needs an Annual Service</h2>
      <p class="pf-sub">Carbon monoxide safety. Warranty protection. Lower bills on larger heating systems. Early fault detection. For Formby's bigger properties, an unserviced system costs more to run and more to repair.</p>
      <div style="margin-top:2rem;">
        <div class="pf-pros">
          <h3 style="text-align:center;">What an Annual Service Protects</h3>
          <ul class="pf-check-list">
            <li>Carbon monoxide safety. A serviced boiler has its flue and combustion checked by a Gas Safe engineer. CO has no smell and no colour. Annual testing is the only reliable way to confirm your boiler is not producing CO. Particularly important for larger Formby properties where the boiler may be in a utility room remote from living spaces</li>
            <li>Manufacturer warranty maintained. Worcester Bosch and Vaillant both require annual servicing by a Gas Safe engineer and an updated Benchmark certificate to keep the warranty valid. Missing one year can void a 10-year warranty regardless of boiler age</li>
            <li>Lower gas bills on larger heating systems. A Formby property running a system boiler, multiple zones and underfloor heating uses significantly more gas than a standard home. A 10 to 15% efficiency loss on an unserviced boiler of this scale has a meaningfully larger financial impact than on a small combi property</li>
            <li>Inhibitor maintained across a larger system. A Formby multi-zone system has more pipework, more radiators and a larger surface area requiring inhibitor protection. The inhibitor degrades across this larger system and must be tested and topped up annually</li>
            <li>Cylinder safety components checked. Pressure relief valves, expansion vessels and temperature valves on unvented cylinders have defined service lives. Annual inspection by a G3 engineer confirms these components are operating within safe limits</li>
            <li>Annual reminder included. We add you to our reminder list and contact you when the next service is due. You never miss a year and never accidentally void your warranty</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>


  <!-- WHAT IS CHECKED -->
