        <div class="pf-who-item pf-who-yes"><span class="pf-who-icon">✓</span><div><strong>Gas pressure and flow rate</strong><p>Gas supply pressure and flow rate confirmed correct for the boiler's operating specification.</p></div></div>
        <div class="pf-who-item pf-who-yes"><span class="pf-who-icon">✓</span><div><strong>Burner and heat exchanger</strong><p>Burner removed and inspected for debris and damage. Heat exchanger checked for corrosion and cracking.</p></div></div>
        <div class="pf-who-item pf-who-yes"><span class="pf-who-icon">✓</span><div><strong>Flue integrity and external condition</strong><p>Full flue route inspected. For Formby coastal properties, external flue terminal checked for salt corrosion and blockage.</p></div></div>
        <div class="pf-who-item pf-who-yes"><span class="pf-who-icon">✓</span><div><strong>Zone valves, pump and motorised valves</strong><p>For system boilers. Zone valve operation, pump condition and flow rate, motorised valve timing and seating. These are the components specific to system boiler configurations common in Formby.</p></div></div>
        <div class="pf-who-item pf-who-yes"><span class="pf-who-icon">✓</span><div><strong>Safety devices tested</strong><p>Pressure relief valve, overheat thermostat and gas valve all tested for correct operation under fault conditions.</p></div></div>
        <div class="pf-who-item pf-who-yes"><span class="pf-who-icon">✓</span><div><strong>Inhibitor tested and topped up</strong><p>Inhibitor concentration tested. Topped up to the correct level across the full heating system. Particularly important in larger Formby multi-zone systems with greater system volume.</p></div></div>
        <div class="pf-who-item pf-who-yes"><span class="pf-who-icon">✓</span><div><strong>Unvented cylinder inspection</strong><p>For properties with unvented cylinders. Pressure relief valve, expansion vessel, temperature and pressure valve, thermostat and immersion heater all checked. Carried out by our G3 qualified engineers only.</p></div></div>
        <div class="pf-who-item pf-who-yes"><span class="pf-who-icon">✓</span><div><strong>Magnetic filter cleaned</strong><p>If a magnetic filter is fitted, cleaned as standard. A blocked filter strains the pump and reduces system efficiency.</p></div></div>
        <div class="pf-who-item pf-who-yes"><span class="pf-who-icon">✓</span><div><strong>Full function test and Benchmark updated</strong><p>Full heating and hot water cycle run across all zones. Benchmark updated. Service certificate and cylinder check record emailed same day.</p></div></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>


