        <div class="pf-who-item pf-who-yes"><span class="pf-who-icon">✓</span><div><strong>Vaillant. Up to 10 years</strong><p>Annual servicing recorded in the Benchmark commissioning checklist required. Failure to service annually voids the extended warranty. We carry Vaillant specialist diagnostic tools on every van.</p></div></div>
        <div class="pf-who-item pf-who-yes"><span class="pf-who-icon">✓</span><div><strong>Ideal Boilers. Up to 10 years</strong><p>Annual servicing by a Gas Safe registered engineer required. Service record retained and Benchmark updated. We carry out full warranty servicing for all Ideal models across Formby.</p></div></div>
        <div class="pf-who-item pf-who-yes"><span class="pf-who-icon">✓</span><div><strong>Baxi. Up to 7 years</strong><p>Annual servicing required. An unserviced boiler that develops a maintenance-related fault will not be covered under warranty. We update the service record on every visit.</p></div></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>


