        <div class="pf-why-item"><h3>System Boiler Service. Same Price.</h3><p>We service system boilers at the same £120 fixed price as combi boilers. No system boiler surcharge. Includes zone valve testing, pump assessment, expansion vessel and all heating circuit controls specific to your system boiler configuration.</p></div>
