        <div class="pf-why-item"><h3>Annual Reminder Included Free</h3><p>We add you to our annual reminder list after your first service. We contact you when the next is due. You never miss a year and never accidentally void your manufacturer warranty.</p></div>
      </div>
      <div style="background:var(--navy);border-radius:10px;padding:2rem;text-align:center;margin-top:2rem;">
